---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Safeguarding Supervision | C&H Safeguarding">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 pt-36 mb-8">
    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row">
      <div class="md:w-1/2 md:pr-8">
        <img
          src="https://placehold.co/600x400"
          alt="Safeguarding Supervision"
          class="md:hidden rounded-lg shadow-lg mb-8"
        />
        <h1
          class="text-3xl md:text-4xl text-center font-bold text-primary mb-6"
        >
          Safeguarding Supervision
        </h1>
        <p class="md:pl-8 text-lg mb-6">
          Specially trained members of our team will provide safeguarding
          supervision to staff as needed. Safeguarding supervision refers to the
          structured support and oversight provided to professionals working
          with vulnerable groups, such as children or at-risk adults.
        </p>
        <p class="md:pl-8 text-lg mb-6">
          The aim is to provide guidance, ensure accountability, and promote the
          well-being and safety of those under their care.
        </p>
        <p class="md:pl-8 text-lg mb-6">
          Supervision can be offered ad-hoc or on a regular basis, in a group or
          one-to-one setting, and either formal or informal.
        </p>
        <a
          href="#"
          class="md:hidden btn btn-primary flex btn-lg items-center justify-center w-full"
        >
          <svg
            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
            class="h-6 w-6 mr-2"
            fill="none"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            stroke="currentColor"
          >
            <path
              stroke-linecap="round"
              stroke-linejoin="round"
              stroke-width="2"
              d="M8 12h.01M12 12h.01M16 12h.01M21 12c0 4.418-4.03 8-9 8a9.863 9.863 0 01-4.255-.949L3 20l1.395-3.72C3.512 15.042 3 13.574 3 12c0-4.418 4.03-8 9-8s9 3.582 9 8z"
            ></path>
          </svg>
          Speak to one of our team
        </a>
      </div>
      <div class="hidden md:block md:w-1/3">
        <img
          src="https://placehold.co/600x400"
          alt="Safeguarding Supervision"
          class="rounded-lg shadow-lg mb-8"
        />
        <a
          href="#"
          class="hidden btn btn-primary md:flex btn-lg items-center justify-center btn-block"
        >
          <svg
            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
            class="h-6 w-6 mr-2"
            fill="none"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            stroke="currentColor"
          >
            <path
              stroke-linecap="round"
              stroke-linejoin="round"
              stroke-width="2"
              d="M8 12h.01M12 12h.01M16 12h.01M21 12c0 4.418-4.03 8-9 8a9.863 9.863 0 01-4.255-.949L3 20l1.395-3.72C3.512 15.042 3 13.574 3 12c0-4.418 4.03-8 9-8s9 3.582 9 8z"
            ></path>
          </svg>
          Speak to one of our team
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
